#. HTML: <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.170" id="170"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.170-187:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an1.170-187:0.2"
msgid "13. Ekapuggalavagga "
msgstr "13. One Person "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.170-187:0.3"
msgid "170 "
msgstr "170 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.22, sc170.1
msgctxt "an1.170-187:170.1.1"
msgid "“Ekapuggalo, bhikkhave, loke uppajjamāno uppajjati bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "“One person, mendicants, arises in the world for the welfare and happiness of the people, out of compassion for the world, for the benefit, welfare, and happiness of gods and humans. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:170.1.2"
msgid "Katamo ekapuggalo? "
msgstr "What one person? "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:170.1.3"
msgid "Tathāgato arahaṃ sammāsambuddho. "
msgstr "The Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:170.1.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, ekapuggalo loke uppajjamāno uppajjati bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānan”ti. "
msgstr "This is the one person, mendicants, who arises in the world for the welfare and happiness of the people, out of compassion for the world, for the benefit, welfare, and happiness of gods and humans.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.171" id="171"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.170-187:170.1.5"
msgid "171 "
msgstr "171 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc171.1
msgctxt "an1.170-187:171.1.1"
msgid "“Ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, pātubhāvo dullabho lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“The appearance of one person, mendicants, is rare in the world. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:171.1.2"
msgid "Katamassa ekapuggalassa? "
msgstr "What one person? "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:171.1.3"
msgid "Tathāgatassa arahato sammāsambuddhassa. "
msgstr "The Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:171.1.4"
msgid "Imassa kho, bhikkhave, ekapuggalassa pātubhāvo dullabho lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "This is the one person, mendicants, whose appearance is rare in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.172" id="172"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.170-187:171.1.5"
msgid "172 "
msgstr "172 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc172.1
msgctxt "an1.170-187:172.1.1"
msgid "“Ekapuggalo, bhikkhave, loke uppajjamāno uppajjati acchariyamanusso. "
msgstr "“One person, mendicants, arises in the world who is an incredible human being. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:172.1.2"
msgid "Katamo ekapuggalo? "
msgstr "What one person? "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:172.1.3"
msgid "Tathāgato arahaṃ sammāsambuddho. "
msgstr "The Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:172.1.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, ekapuggalo loke uppajjamāno uppajjati acchariyamanusso”ti. "
msgstr "This is the one person, mendicants, who arises in the world who is an incredible human being.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.173" id="173"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.170-187:172.1.5"
msgid "173 "
msgstr "173 "

# NOTE: BB has “lament” here. But this topic is treated in more detail at DN 29, where it is not the emotional response that is primary (unlike say DN 16), but their regret at not asking questions when they had the chance. Thus anutappa has its usual sense of “regret”.
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc173.1
#. VAR: anutappā → ānutappā (si)
msgctxt "an1.170-187:173.1.1"
msgid "“Ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, kālakiriyā bahuno janassa anutappā hoti. "
msgstr "“The death of one person, mendicants, is regretted by many people. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:173.1.2"
msgid "Katamassa ekapuggalassa? "
msgstr "What one person? "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:173.1.3"
msgid "Tathāgatassa arahato sammāsambuddhassa. "
msgstr "The Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:173.1.4"
msgid "Imassa kho, bhikkhave, ekapuggalassa kālakiriyā bahuno janassa anutappā hotī”ti. "
msgstr "This is the one person, mendicants, whose death is regretted by many people.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.174" id="174"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.170-187:173.1.5"
msgid "174 "
msgstr "174 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc174.1
msgctxt "an1.170-187:174.1.1"
msgid "“Ekapuggalo, bhikkhave, loke uppajjamāno uppajjati adutiyo asahāyo appaṭimo appaṭisamo appaṭibhāgo appaṭipuggalo asamo asamasamo dvipadānaṃ aggo. "
msgstr "“One person, mendicants, arises in the world unique, without peer or counterpart, incomparable, matchless, unrivaled, unequaled, without equal, the best of bipeds. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:174.1.2"
msgid "Katamo ekapuggalo? "
msgstr "What one person? "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:174.1.3"
msgid "Tathāgato arahaṃ sammāsambuddho. "
msgstr "The Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:174.1.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, ekapuggalo loke uppajjamāno uppajjati adutiyo asahāyo appaṭimo appaṭisamo appaṭibhāgo appaṭipuggalo asamo asamasamo dvipadānaṃ aggo”ti. "
msgstr "This is the one person, mendicants, who arises in the world unique, without peer or counterpart, incomparable, matchless, unrivaled, unequaled, without equal, the best of bipeds.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="175-186" id="175"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.170-187:174.1.5"
msgid "175–186 "
msgstr "175–186 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.23, sc175.1
msgctxt "an1.170-187:175.1.1"
msgid "“Ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, pātubhāvā mahato cakkhussa pātubhāvo hoti, mahato ālokassa pātubhāvo hoti, mahato obhāsassa pātubhāvo hoti, channaṃ anuttariyānaṃ pātubhāvo hoti, catunnaṃ paṭisambhidānaṃ sacchikiriyā hoti, anekadhātupaṭivedho hoti, nānādhātupaṭivedho hoti, vijjāvimuttiphalasacchikiriyā hoti, sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyā hoti, sakadāgāmiphalasacchikiriyā hoti, anāgāmiphalasacchikiriyā hoti, arahattaphalasacchikiriyā hoti. "
msgstr "“With the appearance of one person, mendicants, there is the appearance of a great eye, a great light, a great radiance, and the six unsurpassable things; the realization of the four kinds of textual analysis; the penetration of many and diverse elements; the realization of the fruit of knowledge and freedom; the realization of the fruits of stream-entry, once-return, non-return, and perfection. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:175.1.2"
msgid "Katamassa ekapuggalassa? "
msgstr "What one person? "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:175.1.3"
msgid "Tathāgatassa arahato sammāsambuddhassa. "
msgstr "The Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:175.1.4"
msgid "Imassa kho, bhikkhave, ekapuggalassa pātubhāvā mahato cakkhussa pātubhāvo hoti, mahato ālokassa pātubhāvo hoti, mahato obhāsassa pātubhāvo hoti, channaṃ anuttariyānaṃ pātubhāvo hoti, catunnaṃ paṭisambhidānaṃ sacchikiriyā hoti, anekadhātupaṭivedho hoti, nānādhātupaṭivedho hoti, vijjāvimuttiphalasacchikiriyā hoti, sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyā hoti, sakadāgāmiphalasacchikiriyā hoti, anāgāmiphalasacchikiriyā hoti, arahattaphalasacchikiriyā hotī”ti. "
msgstr "This is the one person whose appearance brings the appearance of a great eye, a great light, a great radiance, and the six unsurpassable things; the realization of the four kinds of textual analysis; the penetration of many and diverse elements; the realization of the fruit of knowledge and release; the realization of the fruits of stream-entry, once-return, non-return, and perfection.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.187" id="187"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.170-187:175.1.5"
msgid "187 "
msgstr "187 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc187.1
msgctxt "an1.170-187:187.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekapuggalampi samanupassāmi yo evaṃ tathāgatena anuttaraṃ dhammacakkaṃ pavattitaṃ sammadeva anuppavatteti yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, sāriputto. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single other person who rightly keeps rolling the supreme Wheel of Dhamma that was rolled forth by the Realized One like Sāriputta. "

msgctxt "an1.170-187:187.1.2"
msgid "Sāriputto, bhikkhave, tathāgatena anuttaraṃ dhammacakkaṃ pavattitaṃ sammadeva anuppavattetī”ti. "
msgstr "Sāriputta rightly keeps rolling the supreme Wheel of Dhamma that was rolled forth by the Realized One.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.170-187:187.1.3"
msgid "Ekapuggalavaggo terasamo. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></section></body></html>
